data.title: Mtn Doodle
data.meta_description: Breeding the best F1, F1b, & Multigen Standard Mini Toy and Micro Bernedoodles in California! Tricolor & Merle.
data.text:
SIZE: Our Aussie-Mountain Doodles aka "AMDs" come in four different sizes. Our Medium AMDs are 35-50lbs, Mini AMDs are 25-35lb, our Toy AMDs are 15-25lbs & occasionally we will have an even smaller Micro AMD at 5-15lb. They have a stocky square frame and teddy bear face. AMDs can be higher % Bernese to lower % Aussie, higher % Aussie to lower % Bernese, or near equal. Each litter is a unique blend! NEW Parents coming in 2024!

COAT: The Sunny Ridge Aussie-Mountain Doodles are created by breeding a Bernedoodle to an Aussiedoodle in a variety of generational blends. This means all puppies are considered "multigen" and not F1 or F1b etc. We have carefully selected and paired our parent dogs with health, structure, & genetics in mind. They have low-nonshedding coats in wavy or curly, and a RAINBOW of color including Merle, Chocolate, Tricolor, & Red!

TEMPERAMENT: Intelligent, balanced, affectionate and loyal. These special Doodles give the best of all 3 breeds! They're athletic and capable of keeping up with any lifestyle while maintaining a more laid-back personality. They're trainable and willing to learn and but are more at ease just lounging around. They're a perfect blend of Aussiedoodle & Bernedoodle!

FUN FACTS: Aussie-Mountain Doodles are one of our FAVORITE breeds of puppy to raise! We really enjoy their balanced temperaments and how quickly they learn new things.

PRICING: $3,500 - $5,000. A litters generation, size, overall quality of coat/genetics, individual markings- parti, minimal tri or classic tuxedo, & intensity of point color & eye color are all factors in pricing. Puppies are not officially priced until 3-4 weeks old.

*Puppies with exceptional color markings & coat may exceed this range.
